</span>
        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type">int</span>
    </dt>
    <dd>The maximum number of nodes unavailable at once during a version update. Nodes will be updated in parallel. This value or maxUnavailablePercentage is required to have a value.The maximum number is 100.</dd><dt class="property-optional"
            title="Optional">
        <span id="maxunavailablepercentage_csharp">

</span>
        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type">int</span>
    </dt>
    <dd>The maximum percentage of nodes unavailable during a version update. This percentage of nodes will be updated in parallel, up to 100 nodes at once. This value or maxUnavailable is required to have a value.</dd></dl>
